                                Anemone
                                
                                
Introduction:
-------------

Anemone is a client for Haven & Hearth. It's based on Xcom's modification of
Ender's client and Groovy Maid scripting engine and provides a number of new 
features as well as some bug fixes and tweaks:

- Multi-session support.
- On-screen FEP bar.
- Targeting.
- Alarms.
- Object's health statuses.
- Graphical bars showing amount or liquid in containers.
- Pathfinding framework.
- Vastly expanded scripting API.
- And a lot more!

Latest version can always be found at https://github.com/romovs/Haven-and-Hearth-Client



References:
-----------

Xcom's client: https://github.com/X-com/Haven-and-Hearth-client-modified-by-Ender/tree/Ender-Edited
Groovy Maid: http://code.google.com/p/hnh-groovy-maid



